name: Doctor Who Weeping Angel Mug
description:

Mugs are dishwasher and microwave safe.  Made in the USA!

name: Tardis Painting on a Ceramic Mug - Black
description:
This is a standard 11 oz black ceramic mug. It has a cool picture of the Tardis, the time traveling police box on it. 

We make all of our mugs after they are ordered, specifically for your order. 

Mugs are UV Protected, FDA Compliant, Microwave and Dishwasher safe. 

The image is permanently sublimated onto the mug. It will never fade, flake, or wash away. The images look amazing. It will come packed safely and securely in a box.
